title: Remove e-mail address from About screen
message:
Remove e-mail address from About screen

I started getting a log of accidental e-mails from users of forks of this app, which do not edit personal information in the AboutActivity.
All forks should update the About page with the fork maintainer's contact details, and link back to the original author's github page.
